cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR, cs.MM 

This paper deals with image-to-image translation, specifically in the context of face editing tasks. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also proposes a novel source classifier and uses it to improve the translation process, which suggests that it could also be relevant to the sub-categories of cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the paper involves generating images, which could fall under cs.GR (Graphics) and cs.MM (Multimedia).
